{
  "stem": "22047.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to be free one of these days, but we've got to wait till people come from the rear-- the medical people and the people with food for you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're going to be spoon fed for a while, 'cause you-- we can't give you a banquet right off or you'll die.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I think the word spread that we were really friends, and we were going to let them go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you know that they cannot be fed with regular food?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we were told that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we got into the camp, the battalion commander that was-- came up behind us-- in fact, there were a lot-- awful lot of folks came up behind us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our job was to-- to get into the camp, keep prisoners in, don't-- don't feed them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were told that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't feed them, because they haven't had any food for a long period of time-- enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had enough to keep them barely alive, those who hadn't died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were told, do not feed them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And do not let them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know that at the time there was anybody alive, because we went into the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was our job, to get inside and close the gate and keep prisoners in, and try to comfort them as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it turned out that one person was alive in those 40 cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how many hundreds of dead bodies were in those cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Turned out one of the sergeants heard a moan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he called the battalion commander-- I think he's Don-- [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Donnard-- ?] he was colonel at the time, Colonel [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Donnard. ?] And a tank destroyer captain came.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
